query:
SELECT 
  scc.supplierId,
  s.companyName,
  scc.countryCode,
  COUNT(DISTINCT sr.id) as total_rates,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT sr.serviceType) as service_types,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT sr.serviceLevel) as service_levels
FROM supplierCoverageCountries scc
INNER JOIN suppliers s ON s.id = scc.supplierId
LEFT JOIN supplierRates sr ON sr.supplierId = scc.supplierId AND sr.countryCode = scc.countryCode
WHERE scc.countryCode = 'AU'
GROUP BY scc.supplierId, s.companyName, scc.countryCode
LIMIT 10;
